,"description":"Put your left hand on your back, use your right hand to grab your left elbow and gently pull it. Hold this position for a few seconds","video":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yAvpW_zKJmI&t=216s"],["Name":"Triceps Stretc Right","image":#imageLiteral(resourceName: "tricep stretch right-1"),"ducration":"30 s","description":"Put your right hand on your back, use your left hand to grab your right elbow and gently pull it. Hold this position for a few seconds.","video":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yAvpW_zKJmI&t=216s"],["Name":"Cat Cow Pose","image":#imageLiteral(resourceName: "cat-cow-pose"),"ducration":"30 s","description":"Start on all fours with your knees under your butt and your hands directly under your shoulders. Then take a breath and make your belly fall down, shoulders roll back and head come up towards the ceiling. As you exhale, curve your back upward and let your head come down. Repeat the exercise.Do it slowly with each step of this exercise","video":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kqnua4rHVVA"],["Name":"Cobra Stretch","image":#imageLiteral(resourceName: "cobra stretch"),"ducration":"30 s","description":"Lie down on your stomach and bend your elbows with your hands beneath your shoulders. Then push your chest up off the ground as far as possible. Hold this position for seconds.","video":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JDcdhTuycOI"],["Name":"Child's Pose","image":#imageLiteral(resourceName: "child pose"),"ducration":"30 s","description":"Start with your knees and hands on the floor. Put your hands a little forward, widen your knees and put your toes together. Take a breath, then exhale and sit back. Try to make your butt touch your heels. Relax your elbows, make your forehead touch the floor and try to lower your chest close to the floor. Hold this position.Keep your arms stretched forward as you sit back. Make sure there is enough space between your shoulders and ears during the exercise","video":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eqVMAPM00DM"],["Name":"Spine Lumbar Twist Stretch left","image":#imageLiteral(resourceName: "spine lumber twist stretch left"),"ducration":"30 s","description":"Lie on your back with your legs extended. Lift your left leg up and use your right hand to pull your left knee to the right, but keep your other arm extended to the side on the floor. Hold this position for a few seconds.","video":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4DUaXUtmCNo"],["Name":"Spine Lumbar Twist Stretch right","image":#imageLiteral(resourceName: "spine lumber twist stretch right"),"ducration":"30 s","description":"Lie on your back with your legs extended. Lift your right leg up and use your left hand to pull your right knee to the left, but keep your other arm extended to the side on the floor. Hold this position for a few seconds.","video":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4DUaXUtmCNo"]]
